en_219486_2	Train services being gazette as an essential service and the emergency law being in effect has resulted in the situation.
en_219486_3	Several employees serving different grades in railway service including railway engine drivers commenced a strike recently standing against the cabinet approved proposals on eliminating salary anomalies, not been brought into effect.
en_219486_4	Later strike action was initiated every Thursday from midnight for a period of 24 hours.
